What a lovely Pilates weekend. 

We are preparing to welcome you all at our Pilates Summer school: Certification for Pilates Mat and Reformer from June 16th to August 8th!

Created as a summer school intensive, we will review Pilates anatomy, alignment and movement principles. 

This comprehensive training program provides an engaging and immersive learning experience led by highly knowledgeable, experienced and supportive instructors. 

Are you excited? Because we are!
